  "text": "The amount of total EPS was determined as described previously [CITATION_1] . Briefly, 1 mL cell cultures grown in M9-0.4% mannitol medium were collected after 48 h and boiled in water for 10 min. The supernatants were then used for an anthrone-H 2 SO 4 assay to determine EPS concentrations. This assay was performed with two independent cultures.",
